SELECT 
    'BidIsSubmitted_' || "AuditEntry"."ID" AS "ID",
    "Bid"."Id" AS "Bid",
    "AuditEntry"."TimeCreated" as "Time"
FROM "o_custom_AuditEntry" as "AuditEntry"
LEFT JOIN "o_custom_Bid" AS "Bid" ON 1=1
    AND SPLIT_PART("ParametersParam2",'{String}',2) =  "Bid"."AlternativeId"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "AuditEntry"."TemplateActionNameDefaultStringTranslation" = 'Bid is submitted'
    AND "AuditEntry"."TimeCreated" IS NOT NULL
